软件包 com.yuep.core.facade.def

接口摘要
FacadeManager Title: FacadeManager Description:管理facade
FacadeProcessor Title: FacadeProcessor Description: Facade的处理器，可以被替换
RemoteInvocationFacade Title: RemoteInvocationFacade Description: 远程调用统一的转发服务
 

类摘要
AbstractFacadeProcessor Title: AbstractFacadeProcessor Description: 对FacadeProcessor进行扩展的抽象基类，提供了最简单的默认实现
FacadeResponse Title: FacadeResponse Description: facade调用中返回对象,包括返回值与异常,是否需要强制返回,类似于holder
 

异常摘要
FacadeException Title: FacadeException Description: Facade使用的异常类
